thread.title: BRIEF-Moody's Says Morocco's Credit Profile Reflects Move Towards Value-Added Exports, Fiscal Progress

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Moody's Says Morocco's Credit Profile Reflects Move Towards Value-Added Exports, Fiscal Progress
text:
March 5 (Reuters) - Moody’s:
* MOODY’S SAYS MOROCCO’S CREDIT PROFILE REFLECTS MOVE TOWARDS VALUE-ADDED EXPORTS AND FISCAL PROGRESS
* MOODY’S SAYS MAIN CONSTRAINTS ON MOROCCO’S RATING ARE RELATIVELY LOW GDP PER CAPITA, VOLATILE GROWTH PATTERN, RELATIVELY HIGH, BUT AFFORDABLE, DEBT-TO-GDP RATIO
* ‍MOODY’S SAYS A “WEAK” LABOUR MARKET AND SKILLS MISMATCHES LIMIT MOROCCO’S COMPETITIVENESS, CONSTRAIN POTENTIAL GROWTH​ Source text for Eikon:
